 " government credit guarantee "  refers to all types of guarantees covering debt service obligations of 
beneficiaries and, as such, includes government guarantees issued for bonds as well. 7,8 However, this 
study categorised credit guarantees issued within the framework of PPP projects within a different 
group to be discussed subsequently. In this conceptual framework, government credit guarantees 
